      "text": "test.discover tests in \u0027_timeout\u0027 recursive, pattern=\u0027*.fixture.goal\u0027, write to %tests%",
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "indent": 0,
      "comment": "Discover a fixture that sleeps 30 seconds, run with test.run timeout=1.\nThe fixture must come back with Status=Timeout \u2014 proves test.run cancels\nthe child via CancellationToken and maps the cancellation to TestStatus.Timeout\nrather than hanging the parent.",
